{"tid":692824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★日本「奴隸監測app」監測職員每日步行數","createTime":"2018-06-07T03:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:41:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7cd782873c59907eb50417be4cc31d6845b755","tid":692824,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.jobmarket.com.hk/JM2Image/JM2images_old/Bastille/259c3935-ed25-431b-974a-220f9c9ee079.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobmarket.com.hk%2FJM2Image%2FJM2images_old%2FBastille%2F259c3935-ed25-431b-974a-220f9c9ee079.png&h=ccc3899e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本有公司研發「奴隸監測app」，目的是為了提升員工的工作動力。此應用程式是為新入職職員而設，由於新入職員工初接觸工作，因此未能在短時間做出實績，有機會被上司誤會而挨罵，此程式便能讓老闆透過員工的步行總數得知員工有否「蛇王」，減少被責罵的機會。<br />\n<br />\n 「奴隸監測app」主要對象是需要外出「跑數」的營業員公司。這個程式能紀錄員工的每一步，同時亦會顯示你的公司內的排名、研發公司負責人更表示這程式設立了全國排名，只有有導入這程式的公司其員工均自動參與此排名，比較一日內日本全國步行數最高的營業員。程式是旨在透過遊戲形式，炒熱公司內的工作氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jobmarket.com.hk/JM2Image/JM2images_old/Bastille/9168990b-ccd1-4edf-9c64-d1f45c461bdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobmarket.com.hk%2FJM2Image%2FJM2images_old%2FBastille%2F9168990b-ccd1-4edf-9c64-d1f45c461bdc.png&h=3b1e7143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而，此程式引起了不少網民的熱烈討論，許多網民對「步數管理」功能帶有意見，認為這會造成「過於苛刻的勞動」、「將行動監視形式化」、「工作環境惡化」等問題。有網民更表示不少員工步行數非常高，但業績卻沒有增長，認為這程式未能確實反映員工的工作能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jobmarket.com.hk/bastille/%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E6%82%B2%E5%93%80%EF%BC%81%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B8%E7%9B%A3%E6%B8%ACapp%E3%80%8D%E7%9B%A3%E6%B8%AC%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobmarket.com.hk%2Fbastille%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%2582%25B2%25E5%2593%2580%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A5%25B4%25E9%259A%25B8%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%25B8%25ACapp%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2595%25B8&d=Q%2BIWNMT%2BEZtgSICJ8Jsi1pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=992e41b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jobmarket.com.hk/bastille/%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E6%82%B2%E5%93%80%EF%BC%81%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B8%E7%9B%A3%E6%B8%ACapp%E3%80%8D%E7%9B%A3%E6%B8%AC%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B8</a>"},{"pid":"a8494ae4b821d1dfdeadec026a0384871ca8a955","tid":692824,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb564e87206a274b77b951354fd9278bceb91dc","tid":692824,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"老貓love this"},{"pid":"72587014ab41d13a6ea351261a9758ebaca47a33","tid":692824,"uid":134997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"不如直接插塊晶片入個腦度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835fe26c451e5cb20a6277d8a39be24b3641a536","tid":692824,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fb564e87206a274b77b951354fd9278bceb91dc","tid":692824,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"老貓love this"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44679312aec2711967236aa86a24e